<L>__{interior building basement corridor continuing}
<A>__{o'ryan turns a corner, vanishing. mackelway follows.}
<L>__{interior building corridor corner continuing}
<A>__{mackelway finds himself facing another endless corridor: one door after another, for what seems like a mile. but no o'ryan. then mackelway spots an exit sign. a stairwell...}
<L>__{interior stairwell continuing}
<A>__{mackelway enters. the stairs go six stories up from here... and one story down. a sub basement. it's a guess. he descends, gun drawn.}
<L>__{interior sub basement continuing}
<A>__{mackelway emerges. "b 2" looks a lot like b 1: long and endless. we hear air moving around us, pipes carrying water, the wheezing of an old generator... and, on all sides of us, dooes, a mile of them: maintenance offices, supply rooms, labs. he opens one a janitor's supply. no one in here. tries another door. locked. a second. locked. a third. locked. air sucks through a corridor around us. he thinks he hears footsteps around a corner. runs at them.}
